{"ts":1772778924227,"data":{"date":"2024-05-23","platform":"游戏","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/2e/ef/385208_shW2q.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/2e/ef/385208_shW2q.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/2e/ef/385208_shW2q.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/2e/ef/385208_shW2q.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/2e/ef/385208_shW2q.jpg"},"summary":"漂泊者，欢迎在这个时代醒来。\r\n这是抗争的时代。自百年之前的悲鸣开始，前所未见的存在浮现于世界之上，引发灾难与战乱在大地上肆虐。这一纪文明，曾一度滑落到毁灭边缘。\r\n这也是建设的时代。从黑暗中活下来的人类携手终结了与同类和异种的漫长战争，在面目全非的陌生大地上重建家园。从旧日辉煌中寻找到的希望，在建设者的手中化为了全新的城市与工厂，奏响复兴的长歌。\r\n而你，久远文明的漂泊者，不论是什么让你苏醒，都欢迎来到这片危险而又激荡的天地。有很多战斗等待你吹响号角，有很多秘密静待你昭告天下，还将有很多伙伴迎来与你的宿命相逢。\r\n你们的传说，注定将要汇成人类文明的新一轮壮阔浪潮。","name":"鸣潮","name_cn":"鸣潮","tags":[{"name":"库洛游戏","count":215,"total_cont":0},{"name":"手游","count":204,"total_cont":0},{"name":"开放世界","count":203,"total_cont":0},{"name":"国产","count":169,"total_cont":0},{"name":"ARPG","count":123,"total_cont":0},{"name":"PC","count":116,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2024","count":86,"total_cont":0},{"name":"游戏","count":51,"total_cont":0},{"name":"ACT","count":46,"total_cont":0},{"name":"Windows","count":37,"total_cont":0},{"name":"原神2.0","count":35,"total_cont":0},{"name":"iOS","count":28,"total_cont":0},{"name":"米池","count":24,"total_cont":0},{"name":"Android","count":22,"total_cont":0},{"name":"PS5","count":21,"total_cont":0},{"name":"二游","count":10,"total_cont":0},{"name":"吃不到饭那也不能吃屎啊","count":9,"total_cont":0},{"name":"Mac","count":8,"total_cont":0},{"name":"Mobile","count":7,"total_cont":0},{"name":"抽卡","count":7,"total_cont":0},{"name":"垃圾","count":6,"total_cont":0},{"name":"剧情","count":5,"total_cont":0},{"name":"库洛","count":5,"total_cont":0},{"name":"二次元","count":5,"total_cont":0},{"name":"RPG","count":4,"total_cont":0},{"name":"抄袭","count":4,"total_cont":0},{"name":"有男不玩","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"手遊","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"科幻","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"动作","count":3,"total_cont":0}